(86, 127, 'margaret weiter', 'mweiter@bellsouth.net', '', '184.45.56.197', '2012-03-07 18:38:17', '2012-03-07 18:38:17', 'Mr Davis, I do not believe speedbumps are necessary on Woodmont at this time. My husband, Charles Weiter and I have lived in the Park for 40 years and do not recall a serious accident on Woodmont. Speed bumps would just become an inconvience for the people living in the Park who must use the streets daily and also cheapen the neighbor.  Perhaps sidewalks are a better solution to the problem. We feel that a survey of the residents of the Park should at least be taken to find out how the majority of people feel about installing speed bumps. Thank you for this consideration.', 0, '1', 'Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; MSIE 9.0; Windows NT 6.1; Trident/5.0)', '', 0, 0),
