(62, 1, '2011-09-27 19:47:02', '2011-09-27 19:47:02', 'The City of St. Regis Park has no jurisdiction over the drainage and sewer services provided within the City. Total responsibility for these services and problems is assumed by the Metropolitan Sewer District. These services are paid for by an addttion to your Louisville Water Company bill. The number for the Metropolitan Sewer District is contained in this brochure. If a problem continues to exist after initial contact with MSD, it may be possible for a City official to intercede on your behalf. Please try the Metropolitan Sewer District trouble line first.', 'Sewer, Drainage Problems', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sewer-drainage-problems', '', '', '2011-09-27 19:47:02', '2011-09-27 19:47:02', '', 0, 'http://www.stregispark.net/?page_id=62', 0, 'page', '', 0),
