(68, 1, '2011-09-27 19:48:20', '2011-09-27 19:48:20', 'The City of St. Regis Park provides for the regular resurfacing and repair of the City streets. Please call the city office phone number if you observe a particular problem or pothole on a city street. The City is also responsible for traffic signs. When utilizing traffic or utility poles for "lost dog or cat"  or yard sale signs, we request that all such signs be removed within one week and without damage to the poles.\r\n\r\nLouisville Gas and Electric maintains all street lights within the City. If you notice a street light that is out or in need of repair please contact LG&amp;E at the number listed in this brochure or call the city office.\r\nThe City provides for the salting and sanding and snow removal from streets based on established crtiteria set by the Mayor and the City Council. The service is provided by private contract to the City. If you experience a problem during the snow and ice season please call the City office or the City official overseeing City Services.', 'Street Signs, Lights, and Road Maintenance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'street-signs-lights-and-road-maintenance', '', '', '2011-09-27 19:48:20', '2011-09-27 19:48:20', '', 0, 'http://www.stregispark.net/?page_id=68', 0, 'page', '', 0),
