(85, 1, '2011-10-11 14:09:53', '2011-10-11 14:09:53', 'If you are a new resident of St. Regis Park or a longer term resident, welcome to our web page. We believe our City is a wonderful place to live. The City of St. Regis Park was first incorporated in 1953. It is a 4th Class City with over 600 homes. As a 4th Class City, St. Regis Park has control over development and zoning , the ability to raise revenue thru taxation, and possesses police powers.\n\nHere you will find news about the City, basic information on a wide variety of topics and ways in which you can contact City officials with any comments, questions or problems you may have. Most important of all, this City web site, like the City’s government itself, is for <em>you!</em> Let us know how we can help you in any way.', 'Welcome', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-autosave', '', '', '2011-10-11 14:09:53', '2011-10-11 14:09:53', '', 2, 'http://www.stregispark.net/index.php/2011/10/11/2-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
