on to the assessed value of your property and want to appeal it, you must contact the Jefferson County Property Valuation Administrator. The telephone number for the Jefferson County Property Valuation Administrator is included with the list of telephone numbers contained in this brochure.', 'Taxes', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '50-revision-5', '', '', '2011-10-14 14:05:48', '2011-10-14 14:05:48', '', 50, 'http://www.stregispark.net/index.php/2011/10/14/50-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
