n the ballot in November. For more information contact the Board of Elections at 574-6100.\r\n\r\nThe City Council meets on the 1st Tuesday of every month at 7:30 p.m.. The meetings are held at the McMahan Fire District, 4318 Taylorsville Road. Notices of the meetings are published in the monthly newsletter. The meetings are open to the public and your comments are welcome during Citizen Participation at the beginning of every City Council meeting.', 'Council', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '10-revision-68', '', '', '2011-11-15 19:50:14', '2011-11-15 19:50:14', '', 10, 'http://www.stregispark.net/index.php/2011/11/15/10-revision-68/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
