(309, 1, '2012-08-29 17:25:25', '2012-08-29 17:25:25', 'CITY OF ST. REGIS PARK - CITY COUNCIL MEETING AGENDA\n\n\nCALL TO ORDER\nROLL CALL:\nMAYOR’S REMARKS:\nGUEST: Teague Ridge, Democratic Candidate for Metro Representative,  District 18\nFINANCIAL REPORT: August 2012 - vote\nMINUTES: Regular Council Meeting, August 7, 2012 - vote\nPOLICE REPORT:\nCITATION OFFICER’S REPORT:\nCITY ATTORNEY’S REPORT:\nCITY ENGINEER’S REPORT:\n1.	Status of ADA sidewalk ramp revision project\n2.	Status of storm water flow on roadways\n\nCOUNCIL MEMBERS’ REPORTS:\n\nOLD BUSINESS:\n1.	Status of curb and house number painting\n2.	Street sign poles painting\n3.	Status of Rental Property Information Form distribution\n4.	Second Reading of Proposed Ordinance Regarding Vacancies on the Council\n5.	St. Regis Park city-wide yard sale, Saturday, September 8\n6.	Status of formation of 60th Anniversary Celebration Committee\n7.	Status of St. Regis Park golf shirts and sweatshirts\n8.	Disposal of surplus city property\n    a.  emachines 3000+ AMD Athlon XP computer with 160 GB hard drive\n    b.  emachines keypad with mouse\n    c.  Samsung SyncMaster 712N monitor\n    d.  HP LaserJet 1012 printer\n    e.  Brother Fax – 575 fax machine\n	\nNEW BUSINESS:\n1.	Ordinance issues:\n    a.	Above ground swimming pools\n    b.	Commercial vehicles\n    c.	Driveways\n    d.	Parking on both sides of the street\n    e.	Side yard fences\n    f.	Garages\n    g.	Other ordinances\n2.	Board of Zoning Adjustment hearing (4301 Mt. Vernon Road)\n3.	Maintenance of area between sound barrier wall and privacy fences along I-64\n\nCITIZEN PARTICIPATION:\n\nADJOURN\n\nWe have updated the city ordinances in pdf form <a href="http://www.stregispark.net/ordinances/" title="Ordinances">here.</a>\n', 'September City Council Meeting Agenda', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '307-revision', '', '', '2012-08-29 17:25:25', '2012-08-29 17:25:25', '', 307, 'http://www.stregispark.net/307-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
